commit.message:
stl_tree.h (erase(iterator), [...]): Remove inline specifier.

2010-06-23  Paolo Carlini <paolo.carlini@oracle.com>

	* include/bits/stl_tree.h (erase(iterator), erase(const_iterator)):
	Remove inline specifier.
